description: Who do you prefer to follow on social media? People that are raw and real, or people that only show the best times in their life and use all the filters, or someone in between? Today we're talking about the good the bad and the ugly when it comes to filters, instagram, social media etc. Watch us on YouTube! Search Yeah No I Know on Kristen Leanne's channel
